		</div>
		<h1>DMDX Interface</h1>
		<h2>Create your DMDX configuration files easily.</h2>
		<div id="buttons-pannel"><p>Create a <button type="button" name="" value="" class="css3button" onclick="window.location.href='/header/index'">New Proyect</button></p>
		<p>or</p>
