					<h3>References</h3>
					<p>In this <a href="/home/references_page">page</a> you can see the references to the external sources used in the proyect.</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="footer" id="topfooter">
			<small>Made by Julen Telleria</small>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
